-- China's Hu Jintao Says Country's Yuan Policy Is Responsible, Figaro Says
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   R i c h a r d s
-- 2010-11-01T22:00:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/china-s-hu-jintao-says-country-s-yuan-policy-is-responsible-figaro-says.html
China’s Hu Jintao said the country’s
currency policy is coherent and responsible, Le Figaro reported,
citing an interview with the president. China is working to
maintain relative stability for the yuan at a reasonable and
balanced level, according to the report.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
